high_descs: Turn right to face the table.
Pick up the lettuce on the table, next to the bread.
Turn around and go forward with the counter, then turn left and go to the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the lettuce inside and chill it, then take the lettuce out.
Turn around and go to the sink.
Put the lettuce in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put cold lettuce in the sink.

high_descs: Turn right and walk over to the wooden table.
Pick up the head of lettuce that is closest to the loaf of bread on the wooden table.
Turn around and walk over to the counter, then turn left and walk up to the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the head of lettuce inside, then close the fridge, after a couple second open the fridge back up and take out the now chilled head of lettuce, then close the fridge.
Turn around and walk over to the sink.
Put the chilled head of lettuce into the sink basin.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled head of lettuce in the sink.

high_descs: Pick of the lettuce from the table.
Take the lettuce to the fridge.
Put it in the fridge then take back out.
Take the chilled lettuce to the sink.
Put the chilled lettuce in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Chill the lettuce from the table then put it in the sink.
